                     TOOLS! TOOLS! TOOLS!                                       Most great adventurers are aware of wearing certain items in certain places.    Armor, helms and shields are worn for protection. Weapons are worn in the       fighting hand, usually the right hand. Larger tools also work like this.        END                                                                             Two common tools that must be readied like a weapon are the grappler and        the shovel. The worker can then make use of the ice or dirt before him...       END                                                                             ...which ever the case may be.                                                  FINISH                                                                          